                    subtitle: Text(spots[index].address),
                    trailing: Icon(Icons.check),
                  );
                },
              ),
            ),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}

class ParkingSpot {
  final String name;
  final String address;
  final String lat;
  final String lon;
